metadata.name: AAYC #1
metadata.description: Every good NFT story starts with an image. This collection is based on the famous BAYC Apes using lovely hand-drawn traits (168 exactly). After drawing 80 hours on the toilet - we are ready for the mint. We will use a free mint (no whitelist) solution. You can claim 1 free mint per Wallet until all 10k are gone. Support and get up to 10 for 0.004 eth / nft. We will claim the first 100 Items for the team vault and future promotions.
